#‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ
#‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą
#‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ

#cmd - return : open -a Ghostty

# Swap window with adjacent windows
alt - left  : yabai -m window --swap west; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
alt - right : yabai -m window --swap east; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
alt - up    : yabai -m window --swap north; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
alt - down  : yabai -m window --swap south; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

# Toggle full screen using command + F
ctrl - f : yabai -m window --toggle zoom-fullscreen; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

# Shrink window dimensions using command + M
cmd - m : yabai -m window --resize left:0:-100; yabai -m window --resize top:0:-100; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

# Focus stuff
cmd - j: yabai -m window --focus west; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - l: yabai -m window --focus east; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - i: yabai -m window --focus north; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - k: yabai -m window --focus south; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

# Fix the console key to output tilde (~) regardless of ANSI/ISO hardware
shift - 0x0A : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "~"'
shift - 0x32 : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "~"'

# Map Shift + 3 to output hash (#) instead of ¬£
shift - 3 : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "#"'

#‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ
#‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą
#‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĎ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ

cmd - 1 : yabai -m space --focus 1; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 2 : yabai -m space --focus 2; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 3 : yabai -m space --focus 3; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 4 : yabai -m space --focus 4; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 5 : yabai -m space --focus 5; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 6 : yabai -m space --focus 6; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 7 : yabai -m space --focus 7; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 8 : yabai -m space --focus 8; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 9 : yabai -m space --focus 9; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 0 : yabai -m space --focus 10; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - delete      : yabai -m space --focus 10; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - home        : yabai -m space --focus 11; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - end         : yabai -m space --focus 12; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - pageup      : yabai -m space --focus 13; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - pagedown    : yabai -m space --focus 14; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

cmd - 0x21 : yabai -m space --focus prev; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
cmd - 0x1E : yabai -m space --focus next; sketchybar --trigger window_focus

shift + cmd - 1 : yabai -m window --space 1; yabai -m space --focus 1; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 2 : yabai -m window --space 2; yabai -m space --focus 2; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 3 : yabai -m window --space 3; yabai -m space --focus 3; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 4 : yabai -m window --space 4; yabai -m space --focus 4; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 5 : yabai -m window --space 5; yabai -m space --focus 5; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 6 : yabai -m window --space 6; yabai -m space --focus 6; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 7 : yabai -m window --space 7; yabai -m space --focus 7; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 8 : yabai -m window --space 8; yabai -m space --focus 8; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 9 : yabai -m window --space 9; yabai -m space --focus 9; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - 0 : yabai -m window --space 10; yabai -m space --focus 10; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - delete      : yabai -m window --space 10; yabai -m space --focus 10; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - home        : yabai -m window --space 11; yabai -m space --focus 11; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - end         : yabai -m window --space 12; yabai -m space --focus 12; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - pageup      : yabai -m window --space 13; yabai -m space --focus 13; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces
shift + cmd - pagedown    : yabai -m window --space 14; yabai -m space --focus 14; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces

shift + cmd - 0x21 : wid=$(yabai -m query --windows --window | jq -r '.id'); yabai -m window "$wid" --space prev; yabai -m space --focus prev; yabai -m window --focus "$wid"; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
shift + cmd - 0x1E : wid=$(yabai -m query --windows --window | jq -r '.id'); yabai -m window "$wid" --space next; yabai -m space --focus next; yabai -m window --focus "$wid"; sketchybar --trigger windows_on_spaces; sketchybar --trigger window_focus
